{"tid":45451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小學功課]為何不同時間的影子的方向不同呢？","createTime":"2016-12-19T03:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T06:42:47.000Z","uid":53000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f4eec316ac9bc2a7fd50dbdf66c92fbc53d4406","tid":45451,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q8wrkhfi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq8wrkhfi&h=f793dab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n③為何不同時間的影子的方向不同呢？<br />\n<br />\n答：因為地球會自轉。<br />\n<br />\n錯，需回答太陽會動，東邊升起西邊落下，影子與其方向相對。<br />\n請寫出上課學過的解答。"},{"pid":"7a2421970c7d0ea862a663f093e6e3dca123cbd8","tid":45451,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5880d3d8e92dd9bb58772a77816a4ef926f51448","tid":45451,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:42:20.000Z","msg":"日本都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1058b7d7cffaa1b78c98cbeb1fdd2952c916577","tid":45451,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T03:58:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"83d57585430c508b2984a2f626d9b737b95d15bb","tid":45451,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:00:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48c8f40f65be565077b71ec7793daf6dee118ad","tid":45451,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T04:00:58.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cca6284335b8d955cfb41b410340d8e40cb5